name: Outback Opal Hunters
overview: The world's toughest treasure hunters push their bodies and bank accounts to the limit on a quest to strike it rich, hunting the legendary Queen of Gems - Opal.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Season 3 originally aired on Thursday, October 17, 2019

seasons.name: Season 8
seasons.overview: Australia's toughest treasure hunters are back, taking on the extreme hardship of the Australian outback in pursuit of opal riches.

seasons.name: Season 9
seasons.overview: Australia's toughest treasure hunters are back, taking on the extreme hardship of the Australian outback in pursuit of opal riches.

seasons.name: Season 10
seasons.overview: Australia's toughest treasure hunters are back, taking on the extreme hardship of the Australian outback in pursuit of opal riches.

episodes.name: Opal Fever
episodes.overview:
Rookie Opal Hunters Daniel Becker and Justin Lang leave their families behind, risking it all to chase an opal fortune. Lucky enough to stake a claim on a legendary site known as Shell Patch Reserve, will their luck continue or come to a costly end?

Disc S1 E1 11/15/19

episodes.name: The Sky is Falling
episodes.overview:
Rookies Justin and Daniel tread a dangerous path underground in Coober Pedy, while father-and-daughter mining team Kelly and Al race to stake a claim in Lightning Ridge in an attempt to turn their fortunes around.

Disc S1 E2 11/22/19

episodes.name: The Legend Returns
episodes.overview:
Pete and Mick's mining operation grinds to a sudden halt, while Col's Crew heads underground. The Rookies are in despair until mentor John Dunstan steps in with a last-minute lifeline.

Disc S1 E3 11/29/19

episodes.name: Attack of the Cacti
episodes.overview:
Daniel returns to Coober Pedy a new Dad, determined to find more white opal. Col raises the stakes, forking out thousands on an ancient and dangerous exploration rig, while the Opal Queen and her Dad battle the clock, the weather and a deadly cactus.

Disc S1 E4 12/6/19

episodes.name: Brother vs. Brother
episodes.overview:
It's brother vs. brother as Peter and Mick Cooke go head-to-head in an epic scrapheap challenge to build a monster opal-hunting machine. Meanwhile, the Rookies are forced to start hunting at night.

Disc S1 E5 12/13/19

episodes.name: Rookies are the Bomb
episodes.overview:
Desperate to move more rock, the Rookies get a lesson in the dangerous art of bomb-making. Al and Kelly's lease is up. while Col returns to action after a health scare.

Disc S1 E6 12/20/19

episodes.name: Cave-Ins and Explosions
episodes.overview:
With the end of the season fast approaching, the Rookies risk cave-ins at their abandoned mine claim; deep underground, Bomb King George is trapped in the blast zone.

Disc S1 E7 1/3/20

episodes.name: Aerial Opal Spotting
episodes.overview:
The mining season is almost over. To reach their target, Col's crew takes one last gamble by opal spotting from the air. The Cookes make one final attempt to save their opal machine and the Rookies get lucky.

Disc S1 E8 1/10/20

episodes.name: Rookie Mistakes
episodes.overview:
A new season opal hunting begins! The Rookies face potential disaster from the get go; for Col's Crew, their mining quest is derailed by a serious illness, and the Opal Queen brings in new muscle and new machines for an underground opal hunt.

Disc S2 E1 1/17/20

episodes.name: Wild Wild West
episodes.overview:
Rookie Justin has cracks in his equipment and his relationships. Col's Crew are a man down and on their last drum of fuel. The Fire Crew are on a wild goose chase hunting a bounty of fabled fire opal.

Disc S2 E2 1/24/20

episodes.name: Going Under
episodes.overview:
For the rookies, there's tension as a new partner leads them on a wild-goose chase underground. Plus, the Cooke brothers' season is off to a bad and dangerous start.

Disc S2 E3 1/31/20

episodes.name: Risky Business
episodes.overview:
Rookie Justin gambles thousands of dollars on buying his way out of trouble. Opal queen Kelly needs a big find underground or risks going broke. Aaron and Greg's Dragonfly claim might finally pay off.

Disc S2 E4 2/7/20

episodes.name: Hot Hot Heat
episodes.overview:
The Rookies battle their biggest claim yet, and each other; Col's Crew must bring out the old machines to hunt a new opal seam; and it's heating up as the Fire Crew race a fuel leak, chasing legendary red fire opal.

Disc S2 E5 2/14/20

episodes.name: Machine Mayhem
episodes.overview:
It's last chance for The Rookies' partnership. Col's crew are on a crash course as his reoccurring illness slows them down. The Cooke Brothers fight busted hoses and breakdowns in the quest to strike it rich.

Disc S2 E6 2/21/20

episodes.name: Against All Odds
episodes.overview:
Justin ropes in a stranger in a mad dash to get his excavator across a busy highway. Opal Queen Kelly battles a new claim with a new partner. With Col struck down with illness, Aaron and Greg must push on without him.

Disc S2 E7 2/28/20

episodes.name: Blue Fire Opal or Bust
episodes.overview:
Justin recruits fiancee Becky to save him from financial ruin. The Fire Crew face deadly reptiles and a snapped suspension in search of blue fire opal. The Cooke Brothers go 21 metres under.

Disc S2 E8 3/6/20

episodes.name: Race Against Time
episodes.overview:
The Rookies battle busted hoses and finally hit treasure, while Boulder Boys Aaron and Greg bring in an old monster about to self-destruct. At their wash plant, The Cooke Brothers race to beat the worst drought in a decade.

Disc S2 E9 3/13/20

episodes.name: Desperate Times, Desperate Measures
episodes.overview:
The Rookies, Justin and Becky, risk their lives underground, desperate for a find. Meanwhile opal-hunting legend Col Duff is back, hunting long-forgotten treasure.

Disc S2 E10 3/20/20

episodes.name: Battling Back
episodes.overview:
The Fire Crew's season rests on a knife-edge as they battle their way back from a disastrous setback. The Opal Queen battles rock-hard walls alone, desperate to find opal.

Disc S2 E11 3/27/20

episodes.name: Make or Break
episodes.overview:
Rookie Justin tackles a deal that could make or break him. The Boulder Boys race to save their claim from a monsoon flood, while the Cooke Brothers finally hit pay dirt.

Disc S2 E12 4/3/20

episodes.name: Last Chance
episodes.overview:
It's the end of the mining season and the last chance for the teams. The Rookies gamble their hopes on one last haul of opal, and the Opal Queen makes a final desperate dig.

Disc S2 E13 4/10/20

episodes.name: The Bushmen
episodes.overview: New team The Bushmen clash with opal thieves raiding one of their mines. The Cookes hack an old digging machine, while the Fire Crew hunt for a new deposit of rare black opal.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Season 3 originally aired on Thursday, October 17, 2019

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: In Mintabie, South Australia, The Tunnel Rats are under extra pressure as rival miners close in on their claim. In Sheepyards, NSW, The Bushmen must brave an abandoned mine to remove a dead animal. Meanwhile, rookie prospectors The Poms seek a prize opal to kickstart their mining career.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: The Bushmen face off against a miner who has illegally dug on their claim.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The Tunnel Rats deal with an unexploded bomb and hazardous gases; The Bros attempt to fit their equipment into a new mine; The Poms make their first trip underground.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: In Opalton, Boulder Boys Aaron and Ron's excavator has a close call.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: The Bushmen take a big risk, trying out a new mining method deep below the ground, and injury slows down progress for The Bros and The Poms are struggling to find their first piece of opal.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: The Boulder Boys, who are within reach of their $100,000 season target, chase old leads that could see them strike it rich and The Bushmen face a disaster underground.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A violent summer storm sees The Young Guns race to save their only claim from a flood; meanwhile The McFarlanes must build a drill from spare parts.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Tunnel Rats Bayden Pearse and Leese Grobe get the lifeline they desperately need. Meanwhile, Pete Cooke and Sam Westra are on the last dig of their season, and 20-year-old Sam must decide whether to quit opal mining for good.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: The Australian outback's wildest treasure hunters face even bigger challenges in their quest to strike it rich, as they seek the legendary queen of gems: the opal.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Following six teams across Australia as they search for the country's most iconic gemstone.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: In outback NSW, the worst storm in 20 years devastates the Bushmen's and Chris Cheal's mine; in Coober Pedy, the new team, the Blacklighters, need opal to re-establish

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Pete and Sam begin a risky project that could pay off big time with opal riches; the Bushmen's new equipment doesn't deliver

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The Young Guns spend all of their savings on a hydraulic digger that only causes problems; the Blacklights run out of opal.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The Boulder Boys try to reach a suspected 20-meter-deep opal level by draining floodwater; Rod Manning uses his wife's opal ring as collateral.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Following six teams across Australia as they search for the country’s most iconic gemstone.

episodes.name: Disaster Strikes
episodes.overview:
The Young Guns' season is threatened when JC is injured at a steer riding competition. The Bushmen finally strike opal while digging on the boundary of their claim;. The Cheal's struggle to get to their claim.

Disc S5 E1 6/3/22

episodes.name: The Opal Whisperers
episodes.overview:
Isaac and Sofia -- the Opal Whisperers -- set out to prove themselves as miners. Jaymin and Noah explore a dangerous mine alone while the Blacklighters are hit with a crippling excavator breakdown.

Disc S5 E2 6/10/22

episodes.name: Glory Days
episodes.overview:
Rory and Oscar are forced to operate their dad's 20-tonne drill rig for the first time. The Tarantos are struck down by sickness as they struggle to find Opals on their massive claim, and the Bushmen build a dangerous mine roof.

Disc S5 E3 6/17/22

episodes.name: Young Gun Returns
episodes.overview:
JC returns to White Cliffs after his accident while Blacklight Xavier misses a massive pocket of opal passing through the noodling machine; the Tunnel Rats start their season in a vermin-infested mine.

Disc S5 E4 6/24/22

episodes.name: Trouble Underground
episodes.overview:
The Tarantos' excavator grinds to a halt at the bottom of their mine. The Cheals also face machinery failure as Rory busts their digger underground. The Bushmen's roof is on the edge of collapse.

Disc S5 E5 6/24/22

episodes.name: The Value of Misfits
episodes.overview:
The Misfits give it all they've got to prove their worth in the mine fields of South Australia. The Bishop loses his prized claim to competitors while the Tunnel Rats risk electrocution while operating their digger.

Disc S5 E6 7/1/22

episodes.name: Scrap Noodler
episodes.overview:
Joe and Tash fossick on the surface with hand tools after the Tarantos fails to bring up any color; the Opal Whisperers try constructing a noodler from scrap material while the Misfits narrowly avoid a collapse.

Disc S5 E7 7/1/22

episodes.name: Walls Closing In
episodes.overview:
Machinery woes cause the Cheals to end their opal dreams and consider splitting ways. The Blacklighters move to a new site while Jaymin and JC work alone in claustrophobic tunnels.

Disc S5 E8 7/8/22

episodes.name: Rookie Mistake
episodes.overview: The Bushmen's new rookie rushes into a deadly no-go zone while the Cheals attempt to revive their season; the Mooka Boys try a new technique to expose opal in colorless rock.

episodes.name: Impenetrable No More
episodes.overview: A bomb expert comes in to blast impenetrable rock for the Bishop; the Cheals race to move a rock-extracting blower before heat damages their machine and the Misfits battle avalanches and dust storms.

episodes.name: Follow The Clues
episodes.overview:
Handwritten clues left by Leif's late father help the Mooka Boys hunt for an abandoned mine; the Blacklighters battle choking dust on their dry claim and the Tarantos make emergency repairs on their machine.

Disc S5 E11 7/15/22

episodes.name: Cathedral Secrets
episodes.overview:
Greg explores the hidden tunnels on his massive claim searching for white opal. The Tarantos' excavator springs a leak and the Blacklighters look for a new house.

Disc S5 E12 7/22/22

episodes.name: A Mine That Stings
episodes.overview:
The Bushmen gamble the last of their cash on their first ever drill rig; the Cheals, desperate for a big opal find, face off against turbulent weather; the Mooka boys hunt for treasure in a scorpion-riddled mine.

Disc S5 E13 8/5/22

episodes.name: Sparks Fly
episodes.overview:
The Young Guns face dangerous roads and impenetrable mine walls and faulty electronics spark a fire in the Opal Whisperers' HQ. The Blacklighters risk losing their plan as their generator dies.

Disc S5 E14 8/12/22

episodes.name: Free Falling
episodes.overview:
The Bushmen find a hidden shaft by falling into it and the Blacklighters brand-new investment is dead in the water; a busted jackhammer forces JC and the Young Guns to make emergency repairs halfway down the mine shaft.

Disc S5 E15 8/19/22

episodes.name: Treachery
episodes.overview:
The Bushmen are dismayed after taking over their new recruit's mine and finding it is both treacherous and light on opal; the Bishop turns to explosive means to move a wall; the Misfits work underground for the first time.

Disc S5 E16 8/19/22

episodes.name: Dangers of the Abandoned
episodes.overview:
Scott and the Bishop cause an avalanche while trying to secure a wall. The Mooka Boys' bobcat suffers a critical failure and the Blacklighters dig into a rich and dangerous abandoned mine.

Disc S5 E17 8/26/22

episodes.name: Smashed
episodes.overview:
The Young Guns' hopes of breaking their drought get shattered after they accidentally smash a valuable gemstone; the Bishop loses Scotty underground; the Tarantos' hopes of exposing a rare opal pocket fall in jeopardy.

Disc S5 E18 8/26/22

episodes.name: Digging With A Dinosaur
episodes.overview:
The Misfits prove their worth to Opal Joe with an ancient bulldozer on their last dig; the Opal Whisperers suffer from infighting; the Cheals race against the clock and seasonal storms to rescue their mission.

Disc S5 E19 9/2/22

episodes.name: No Risk, No Reward
episodes.overview:
A massive lightning storm forces the Young Guns to work on a series of flooded dirt roads; the Bushmen risk it all in a dangerous area vandalized by opal thieves; the Blacklighters take their chances with night mining.

Disc S5 E20 9/9/22

8.name: Season 8
8.overview: Australia's toughest treasure hunters are back, taking on the extreme hardship of the Australian outback in pursuit of opal riches.

episodes.name: Start With A Bang
episodes.overview:
Brand new team Digi Diggers bring brand new technology to the opal fields; Josiah and Lisa soon find themselves at breaking point.

The Bushmen bring in an explosives expert to blast through the toughest rock in Grawin; plus, a brand new team brings cutting edge technology to the opal fields.

Disc S6 E1 6/30/23

episodes.name: Baptism By Fire
episodes.overview:
The Cheals take on their most dangerous dig ever.  The Bushmen trial a rookie miner, Ben, to operate their drill to find new opal bearing ground, but he falls short at the first challenge.

Disc S6 E2 7/7/23

episodes.name: In Search of Fuel
episodes.overview:
The Opal Whisperers work underground together for the first time on a claim where million-dollar opal Angel of Yowah was discovered decades earlier. The Mooka Boys are forced to work Leif's late father's abandoned mine.

Disc S6 E3 7/14/23

episodes.name: A Well That Takes on Water
episodes.overview:
The Digi Diggers, Josiah and Lisa, need to explore new ground after mining opal too brittle to sell; they discover their entire claim is at risk of being flooded.

The Digi Diggers need to explore new ground after mining opal too brittle to sell. The Bushmen discover their new claim has been dug out by opal thieves.

Disc S6 E4 7/21/23

episodes.name: Bad Luck
episodes.overview:
The Opal Whisperers are forced to leave behind a rich opal seam in a mine on the verge of collapse; the Cheals are cut off from their mine by crippling floods.

Disc  S6 E5 8/4/23

episodes.name: Start Again From the Beginning
episodes.overview:
Gale-force winds threaten the Digi Diggers' dreams of an eco-mine; the Bushmen discover dangerous old workings while clearing out their new mine; Angel and Joe's search to join the Misfits threatens to tear the team apart.

Disc S6 E6 8/11/23

episodes.name: Hit or Miss
episodes.overview:
The Mooka Boys may lose a potential investor due to their little mining progress, and disaster strikes for the Opal Whisperers when Sofia's hoist fails.

Disc S6 E7 8/18/23

episodes.name: Succession of Opal Joe
episodes.overview:
The Blacklighters discover opalised sea creatures in an ancient seabed; the Cheals close in on their biggest opal haul ever, but all is not as it seems.

Disc S6 E8 8/25/23

9.name: Season 9
9.overview: Australia's toughest treasure hunters are back, taking on the extreme hardship of the Australian outback in pursuit of opal riches.

episodes.name: A Glimmer of Hope
episodes.overview: Mooka Boys brothers Matt and Cozza topple their excavator while attempting to reach a new mine on a treacherous opal field; the Blacklighters are almost buried alive while mining opal in unstable tunnels.

episodes.name: The Reward of the Effort
episodes.overview: A busted dirt hauling bogger bucket threatens the Cheals' ambitions for mammoth back-to-back opal hauls; the Opal Whisperers' partnership with veteran miner Uwe ends abruptly; Angel attempts her first opal sale at the Lightning Ridge Opal Festival.

episodes.name: Soldier of Fortune
episodes.overview: The broke Bushmen are forced to trade opal to get a shaft drilled on a new claim; the Mooka Boys attempt to revive a dump truck and their opal processing plant with disastrous results; the Digi Diggers get lost exploring a terrifying abandoned mine.

episodes.name: The Solar System
episodes.overview: The Digi Diggers get their solar plant installed, but the power-hungry mine triggers a total system shutdown; Lisa jeopardises a sale with a bespoke jeweller designer; Rod goes toe to toe with ratters who stole opal and equipment from their mine.

episodes.name: Light and Shadow
episodes.overview: A vicious storm threatens to end the Misfits' season early; Issy attempts a new black-lighting technique to impress Opal Joe; the Digi Diggers' mine gets flooded, forcing the pair to scour the outback for a new claim.

episodes.name: Honestly Shared
episodes.overview: The Blacklighters must work a new claim using an ancient opal processing plant. The Misfits discover they're losing precious opal, so they attempt a night dig.

episodes.name: Hard on the Edge
episodes.overview: The Bushmen's homemade hoist and bucket fail; Rod is forced to down tools with busted ribs; Sofia and Isaac from "The Opal Whisperers" get trapped at the bottom of their open cut mine in sweltering temperatures.

episodes.name: The Foreign Claim
episodes.overview: Isaac from the Opal Whisperers works an abandoned, dangerous mine and partners up with a veteran Yowah miner; the Mooka Boys are confronted by an irate miner as they peg a claim too close to his mine.

episodes.name: A Barrel Full Of Nuts
episodes.overview: The Bushmen's drill rig loses a vital pin, forcing 74-year-old Les to undertake emergency repairs four meters in the air; the Digi Diggers flooded mine wall collapses as Josiah and Lisa attempt a new method of extracting Yowah nuts.

episodes.name: High Goals
episodes.overview: The Bushmen struggle to locate the source of water flooding their mine; the Misfits are forced to work Issy's mine, Honey Hole, as they wait for bulldozer repairs; the Blacklighters are forced to help a fellow miner on a dangerous night dig.

episodes.name: From the Last Hole
episodes.overview: The Bushmen bust blower pipes and break diggers in their last chance to find opal this season. The team tackle two mines simultaneously and bring in a master opal cutter, hoping to transform rough stones into a $100,000 haul. The Misfits are flooded out of their open cut mine and return to Honey Hole with custom-made machinery; a giant chainsaw attached to a bobcat, desperate to turn a profit on the last dig of their season. Sofia and Isaac from the Opal Whisperers are threatened by a mine roof collapse as they struggle to extract opal from crumbling walls. Isaac attempts to make a profit by cutting and polishing their last opal find for the season, but risks destroying the stones in the process.

episodes.name: The Lucky Day
episodes.overview: Sweltering temperatures and a waterlogged mine threaten to unravel The Digi Diggers' season-long dream; the Cheals' starter motor fails on their wash plant as they race to process the last opal dirt for the season.

episodes.overview: Gross incompetence lands The Blacklighters in hot water with Mark's wife.

episodes.name: Between a Rod and a Hard Place

episodes.name: Ratter Brained
episodes.overview: The Misfits struggle to find an opal king stone for an interstate buyer.

episodes.name: A Chance of Explosives
episodes.overview: Slim Pickings' efforts are derailed by a slipped excavator track.

episodes.name: Dig and Digger
episodes.overview: Sam smashes valuable opal with a jackhammer in the Bushmen's mine.

episodes.name: Boggered
episodes.overview: The Cheals' dreams of expanding their Opal Empire are crushed.

episodes.name: Cheal Be Right
episodes.overview: When Chris suffers a spider bite, Oscar and Luca take up the mining mantle.

episodes.name: Over the Concrete Rainbow
episodes.overview: The Blacklighers are hit with a double dose of disaster.

episodes.name: Red Tape

episodes.overview: Blacklighters Mark L'Anson and Paul Coon get boxed-in during their mission.
